# AI Chat Frontend

A simple web interface for interacting with an AI chatbot.

## Features
- Ask AI questions and get responses.
- Saves Q&A in `localStorage`.
- Displays the latest responses at the top.

## Usage
1. Open `index.html` in a browser.
2. Enter a question and submit.
3. Previous Q&A will be displayed in a scrollable box.

## Technologies
- HTML, CSS, JavaScript
